HEADWORD: Selfless
<hw>Self"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no regard to self;
unselfish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lo now, what hearts have men! they never mount⟦br⟧
As high as woman in her <qex>selfless</qex> mood.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Selflessness</ent>⟦br⟧
